    {
      "text": "Ready 2 Rumble Boxing: Round 2 is a boxing game for the Dreamcast, Nintendo 64, PlayStation, PlayStation 2 (a North American launch title for the system), and Game Boy Advance. It is the sequel to Ready 2 Rumble Boxing.",
      "lang": "en",
      "source": "wikipedia_en"
    },
    {
      "text": "Ready 2 Rumble Boxing: Round 2 est un jeu vidéo de boxe sorti en 2000 et fonctionne sur Dreamcast, PlayStation, PlayStation 2, Nintendo 64 et Game Boy Advance. Le jeu a été développé et édité par Midway.",
      "lang": "fr",
      "source": "wikipedia_fr"
    },
    {
      "text": "Ready 2 Rumble Boxing: Round 2 è un videogioco di pugilato comico sviluppato dalla Midway Games e dalla Point of Wiew Inc. e pubblicato dalla Midway nel 2000 per varie console. È il secondo videogioco della serie Ready 2 Rumble Boxing.",
      "lang": "it",
      "source": "wikipedia_it"
    },
    {
      "text": "Ready 2 Rumble Boxing: Round 2 — симулятор бокса для консолей Dreamcast, Nintendo 64, PlayStation, PlayStation 2 и Game Boy Advance. Сиквел Ready 2 Rumble Boxing.",
      "lang": "ru",
      "source": "wikipedia_ru"
    },
    {
      "text": "『Ready 2 Rumble Boxing: Round 2』は、Dreamcast、Nintendo 64、PlayStation、PlayStation 2（本システムにおける北米ローンチタイトル）、およびGame Boy Advance向けに発売されたボクシングゲームです。これは『Ready 2 Rumble Boxing』の続編にあたります。",
      "lang": "ja",
      "source": "ai_local_gemma4",
      "base_lang": "en"
    }
  ]
